news_header: President Alexander Stubbin and Crown Prince Haakon of Norway conclude their visit in Bergen.
news_text: President Alexander Stubbin and Suzanne Innes-Stuinen's visit to Norway ends today in Bergen. They will first visit the Norwegian Navy's main base in Haakonsvern, followed by a trip to the Port of Bergen. The visit will conclude with a lunch and a walk on Mount Flöyen.
